Create folder <code>/usr/local/etc/onion-grater-merger.d</code>

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/etc/onion-grater-merger.d
}}

Open <code>/usr/local/etc/onion-grater-merger.d/40_bisq.yml</code> with root rights.

{{CodeSelect|code=
kdesudo kwrite /usr/local/etc/onion-grater-merger.d/40_bisq.yml
}}

Paste conents from https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Whonix/onion-grater/master/usr/share/doc/onion-grater-merger/examples/40_bisq.yml into <code>/usr/local/etc/onion-grater-merger.d/40_bisq.yml</code>.

Save.

==== anon-ws-disable-stacked-tor workaround ====
'''On {{gateway_product_name}}.'''

Whonix 14 only. Not required in Whonix 15 and above. <ref>
https://forums.whonix.org/t/bisq-the-p2p-exchange-network/4953/26?u=patrick
</ref>

{{Open with root rights|
filename=/etc/anon-ws-disable-stacked-tor.d/50_user.conf
}}

Paste.

{{CodeSelect|code=
file_port_tuples+=" port#9150:9151 "
}}

Save.

